              <span id="reviewTextContainer83619275" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6110270730958110484">Marvelous story. You have to read it to find out exactly what happens. A fun spoof on religion. The historical detail, the characters, and the humor are enchanting. By the end I loved Brother Cadfael and all the villagers of Gwytherin, Wales. An utterly charming tale and funny too!</span>

          </span>
